overview: Elegant Angel proudly presents the next tease compendium, Just Tease 4, where fans of Elegant Angel's mouth watering scene introductions can acquire a collection of their favorite teases featuring Charley Chase, Asa Akira, Maddy O'Reilly, and many more superstars, all shot in 16:9.
tagline: A little tease never looked so good coming from these beautiful babes!
title: Just Tease 4
